                        <![CDATA[
                        <h1>IT Hardware Sales &amp; Service</h1>
                        <p>Company is a specialized
                                IT Sales Establishment that focuses on providing a diverse selection
                                of IT
                                components for sale. Product contains laptops, RAM, accessories,
                                CCTV
                                Camera and other related items. In addition to product sales,
                                it is
                                also offering installation and repair services for these
                                components.</p>
                        <div data-oe-protected="true"
                                class="o_knowledge_behavior_anchor o_knowledge_behavior_type_toc">
                                <div
                                        class="o_knowledge_toc_content">
                                        <a href="#" data-oe-nodeid="0"
                                                class="oe_unremovable o_no_link_popover d-block o_knowledge_toc_link
                        o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_0">IT
                                                Hardware Sales &amp;
                                                Service</a>
                                        <a href="#" data-oe-nodeid="1"
                                                class="oe_unremovable
                        o_no_link_popover d-block o_knowledge_toc_link
                        o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_1">
                                                Configuration</a>
                                        <a href="#"
                                                data-oe-nodeid="2"
                                                class="oe_unremovable o_no_link_popover d-block
                        o_knowledge_toc_link o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_1">Business
                                                Flow&nbsp;</a>
                                        <a href="#" data-oe-nodeid="3"
                                                class="oe_unremovable o_no_link_popover d-block o_knowledge_toc_link
                        o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_2">Flow
                                                1: Buy Laptop &amp;
                                                Accessories</a>
                                        <a href="#" data-oe-nodeid="4"
                                                class="oe_unremovable
                        o_no_link_popover d-block o_knowledge_toc_link
                        o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_2">Flow
                                                2: B2C eCommerce Sale</a>
                                        <a
                                                href="#" data-oe-nodeid="5"
                                                class="oe_unremovable o_no_link_popover d-block
                        o_knowledge_toc_link o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_2">Flow
                                                3:&nbsp;Bulk
                                                Order</a>
                                        <a href="#" data-oe-nodeid="6"
                                                class="oe_unremovable
                        o_no_link_popover d-block o_knowledge_toc_link
                        o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_2">Flow
                                                4: Installation Service</a>
                                        <a
                                                href="#" data-oe-nodeid="7"
                                                class="oe_unremovable o_no_link_popover d-block
                        o_knowledge_toc_link o_knowledge_toc_link_depth_2">Flow
                                                5: Repair
                                                Service</a>
                                </div>
                        </div>
                        <p>
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <h2>
                                <span
                                        style="font-weight: bolder;">Configuration</span>
                        </h2>
                        <p
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><font
                                                style="color: rgb(255,
                        156, 0);">Product
                                Specification</font>:&nbsp;</strong>Laptops have attributes (Brand,
                                CPU, ...) &amp; variants {RAM, HD)&nbsp;</p>
                        <p
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><font
                                                style="color: rgb(255,
                        156, 0);">Part
                                Code:</font>&nbsp;</strong>Manage unique codes for IT components.</p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;"><strong><font
                                                style="color: rgb(255, 156, 0);">Lot
                                                &amp; Serial Numbers</font>:&nbsp;</strong>Track
                                products with lot and serial numbers.</p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;"><strong><font
                                                style="color: rgb(255, 156, 0);">Warranty
                                                Days</font>:&nbsp;</strong>On products, if you
                                enable "Expiration Date", you can set a warranty duration</p>
                        <p>
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <h2>
                                <span
                                        style="font-size: 24px;">Business
                                        Flow&nbsp;</span>
                        </h2>
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">Flow 1: Buy Laptop
                                &amp; Accessories</h3>
                        <p
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <p
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                                <strong>Purchase Order
                                        Management</strong>
                        </p>
                        <ul style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <li>Create a Request for Quotation to "" for one “<font
                                                class="text-o-color-1">ThinkPad X1 Carbon 35.56cms -
                                        12th Gen Intel
                                                i7</font>”</li>
                                <li>Send the RFQ by
                                        email</li>
                                <li>Once you get the prices&nbsp;from the vendor,
                                        update the prices and lead times and confirm the
                                        order.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <strong>Receipt</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Once the order is confirmed, we are
                                ready to
                                receive it in a few days.</p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">When
                                the shipment&nbsp;arrives &nbsp;with the new products, open the
                                barcode App:</p>
                        <ul style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                                <li>scan a
                                        product from the receipt screen</li>
                                <li>that filters on pending
                                        receipts containing this product</li>
                                <li>pick the right one and
                                        scan the product received</li>
                                <li>scan, or record, the lot
                                        number</li>
                                <li>validate the receipt&nbsp;<br></li>
                        </ul>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Flow 2:
                                B2C eCommerce Sale</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <strong>From
                                        the&nbsp;Ecommerce</strong>
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                                <li>
                                        <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
                                                <font
                                                        color="#212529">Visit the B2C Shop
                                                        Choose&nbsp;products
                                                        and&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>
                                                <font class="text-o-color-1"
                                                        color="#212529">compare</font>
                                                <font color="#212529"> with
                                                        related&nbsp;&nbsp;products. ("</font>
                                                <font
                                                        class="text-o-color-1" color="#212529">ThinkPad
                                                        X1 Nano 33.02cms - 12th
                                                        Gen Intel i7</font>
                                                <font
                                                        color="#212529">","</font>
                                                <font class="text-o-color-1"
                                                        color="#212529">ThinkPad X1 Carbon 35.56cms
                                                        - 12th Gen Intel
                                                        i7</font>
                                                <font color="#212529">"
                                                        ).</font>
                                        </span>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <span
                                                style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
                                                <font
                                                        color="#212529">Finalize the product process
                                                        for the
                                                        checkout.</font>
                                        </span>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <span
                                                style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
                                                <font
                                                        color="#212529">Set the customer to define
                                                        the shipping
                                                        address.</font>
                                        </span>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <span
                                                style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
                                                <font
                                                        color="#212529">Then&nbsp;Pay the
                                                        Order.</font>
                                        </span>
                                </li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>
                                <span
                                        style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
                                        <font
                                                color="#212529">
                                                <b style="font-weight:normal">
                                                        <span
                                                                style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
                        background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal;
                        text-decoration: none;">Later,
                                                                in the Inventory apps, the worker
                                                                uses the
                                                                list of orders to deliver in the
                                                                "Delivery Orders"
                                                                section.</span>
                                                </b>
                                        </font>
                                </span>
                        </p>
                        <h3>
                                <strong>Flow
                                        3:&nbsp;Bulk Order</strong>
                        </h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <strong> B2B Market(Bulk
                                        Order)</strong>
                        </p>
                        <ul style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <li>From the website go to&nbsp;the top menu "Bulk
                                        Order".</li>
                                <li>This customized form will create an opportunity
                                        in the CRM, with the right information.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <p
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                                <strong>Salesperson meet
                                        client</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p>From the CRM, schedule a meeting. As you meet the client, you can create
                                a quotation and <strong>use the
                                        product catalog</strong>. to easily present products to the
                                client and record his order.</p>
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Flow 4:
                                Installation Service</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <strong>Quotation &amp;
                                        Sale</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">To create a quotation, <strong>select the
                                template</strong> "CCTV Installation Setup". That fill in&nbsp;two
                                products:</p>
                        <p
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <ul
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                                <li>CCTV Camera: 1
                                        Unit</li>
                                <li>Installation Service: 1
                                        Unit</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <strong>Confirm Sale Order</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;">As the customer confirms the sale order,
                                one&nbsp;tasks will be created in the 'Installation
                                Project'(Existing).</p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <strong>Deliver products</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;">You can deliver the 1 product("CCTV
                                Camera")
                                from the inventory application. Use the barcode scanner, or the
                                backend, up
                                to you.</p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Warranty date for above product will be
                                calculated from the date of delivery.(<font
                                        class="text-o-color-1">Through Studio, Automated
                                Action-Update Warranty
                                        Date</font>)</p>
                        <blockquote data-o-mail-quote="1"
                                data-o-mail-quote-node="1" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">For the Some
                                Business warranty will start from date of the
                                delivery.</blockquote>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <strong>Installation - CCTV
                                        Camera&nbsp;</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">Assign the Field
                                Service Engineer on the Task of&nbsp;"<font
                                        class="text-o-color-1">Installation Service</font>".</p>
                        <p
                                style="margin-bottom: 0px;">After the planning, field service
                                engineer will visit the client place and start working on
                                installation, they move the task "<font class="text-o-color-1">In
                                Progress</font>" and then "<font class="text-o-color-1">Done</font>"
                                when it's finished and sign the service report.</p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0px;">Flow 5:
                                Repair Service</h3>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">If the product
                                are in warranty and customer has any complaint which need to repair
                                the
                                service. we can repair the product and generate the Invoice if
                                required.</p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 0px;">To do
                                that,</p>
                        <ul style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                                <li>Go to website
                                        and&nbsp;Helpdesk from</li>
                                <li>when open the form choose&nbsp;product ('<font
                                                class="text-o-color-1">ThinkPad X1
                                                Carbon 35.56cms - 12th Gen Intel i7</font>') and
                                        serial number('CNC012345') and submit&nbsp;ticket.</li>
                                <li>support
                                        ticket will be&nbsp;created from backend.</li>
                                <li>open the ticket from backend , system will be displayed Warranty
                                        Date('<font
                                                class="text-o-color-1">24/08/2024</font>') of that
                                        selected serial number(<font class="text-o-color-1">through
                                        Studio</font>).</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <br>
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">
                                <u>Generate Repair Order</u>
                        </p>
                        <p>To do
                                that,&nbsp;</p>
                        <ul>
                                <li>Create the Repair order
                                        from&nbsp;Helpdesk-&gt;Repair Order.</li>
                                <li>Take the
                                        product in our internal location from
                                        customer&nbsp;(WH/Repair).</li>
                                <li>Repair the
                                        product&nbsp;, they move the Order to "Under Repair", and
                                        then
                                        "Repaired" when it's finished.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <blockquote
                                data-o-mail-quote="1" data-o-mail-quote-node="1"
                                style="margin-bottom:
                        0px;">If the product
                                is under warranty then no need to create the invoice and if the
                                product is out of warranty then the user can send the quotation for
                                the repair. Once the customer confirms the rate then the user can
                                start repairing and after the repair we will give the customer an
                                invoice for the same.<br></blockquote>
                        ]]>
                </field>
        </record>
